"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*AfUeN_ZgUsVbVwfk_vvoAg.png)\\n\\n## “WePiggy’s Billionaires” on HECO\\n\\nIn order to encourage users to participate in WePiggy-HECO lending protocol, the WePiggy-HECO “WePigggy’s Billionaires” activity is now open!\\n\\n**Activity time:** 2021/7/28 15:00(UTC+8) to WePiggy’s official launch on the next public chain or layer 2 network\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Activity Rules: \\\\*\\\\*During the activity, participate in WePiggy-HECO WPC mining campaign, and the cumulative amount of mined WPC tokens ranks in the top **198** of the “WePiggy’s Billionaires”, will win the \\\\[HECO Co-branded Edition\\\\] \\\\[Epic Level\\\\] NFT — “**HokagePiggy**”.\\n\\n## **Please note:**\\n\\n1\\\\. The “**HokagePiggy**” NFT will be open for claim after the activity ends. Except for participating in this activity, or through the transfer of old holders in the future, no more “**HokagePiggy**” will be generated.\\n\\n2\\\\. WePiggy reserves the right of final interpretation of this activity.\\n\\n## Activity Participation Tutorial\\n\\n[https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/ylthdl/bgmtwu](https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/ylthdl/bgmtwu)\\n\\n## About “HokagePiggy” NFT\\n\\nThis card is issued to commemorate the third step of WePiggy’s cross-chain deployment plan: HECO.\\n\\nWith the strong wind generated by DeFi, a single spark can start a huge blaze.\\n\\nHolder of this NFT will be blessed by WePiggy with the buff of “Freedom of Wind, Will of Fire”.\",\"timestamp\":1636596798,\"title\":\"WePiggy-HECO “WePiggy’s Billionaires” Activity Begins!\"},\"digest\":\"pf8r-DC5AqPTM5ImeQUkzxHdbFKKl996gphHvQb3KpU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MOToXuaua0SJZ5_SQSsecHvAOLw5KxmLTKhH_Amk1Lw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eHu9Uej8BHwgyRn4jxCzG9EQ1R29cSjilBrFY8fm7pw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"J1LZ